      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for anyone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road. It runs super smoothly and is totally ready for its next big adventure! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
