    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super well-loved over the years. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that still looks great and handles beautifully, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'd love to help you get behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
