    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW's high-revving peak, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. This unit has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a VANOS system refresh and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high cornering loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with updated bushings for crisp turn-in. Finished in a classic colorway, it offers an engaging tactile experience with a linear power band and an exhaust note that only a naturally aspirated straight-six can provide.",
